-- Abu Dhabi Invites Bids for Louvre Construction, Gulf News Says
-- B y   A y e s h a   D a y a
-- 2012-03-25T05:52:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-25/abu-dhabi-invites-bids-for-louvre-construction-gulf-news-says.html
Abu Dhabi ’s Tourism Development &
Investment Co. invited companies to bid for main contract work
for the Persian Gulf emirate’s Louvre museum, according to an
advertisement in Gulf News.  Contractors can request a pre-qualification document for
the project, which includes structural steelwork and mechanical
works, according to the advertisement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
